Package: Rconfigurator
Title: create a Dockerfile of an exactly defined R configuration
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Reinhold",
           family = "Koch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "8436725+reikoch@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Given a recent version number of R and a set of R packages with their version numbers
    create a Dockerfile that implements this R configuration. All standard tests for R and
    the packages will be executed when building the docker image.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
